description:
Have you ever been called a control freak? Are you guilty of controlling people to get what you want? Do you manipulate others into meeting your expectations? Have you used shame, blame, guilt trips, silent treatments, enticements or bribery to get people to say or do what you want? Can you identify the control tactics you use to control others? Learn how to stop being controlling by following the steps outlined in the Bible. Discover how to break free from practicing controlling behavior. 

Watch more: https://adtv.watch/

Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/OfficialADTVChannel?sub_confirmation=1

Visit our website: https://new.amazingdiscoveries.org/
